# Lightning Login Demo App

This app demonstrates Lightning Login (LNURL-auth) for:

1. Non-developers (simple explanation + guided onboarding)

2. Developers (in-depth technical guide + code examples)

3. Live demo (users can actually log in with their Lightning wallet)

4. Workshop Mode (presentation-friendly view)

The app must:

- Be minimal, clean, and easy to extend

- Use Structured Content from /content/*.json for all text content

- Use Next.js App Router

- Use next-auth for session management

- Implement real LNURL-auth using lnurl lib and custom endpoints

- Store users in a small Prisma DB (SQLite for local, Postgres for production)

